ALlQ3HYN0Se5a8T.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498952\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108013122ETAwDgyMPnVXuCrY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498952\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108013123E7fb8raGv04PTSDX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498952\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>伦敦男装周 2019 秋冬于 1 月 7 日落幕 。</strong></p><p>昨日提及，本次男装周共有 5 个中国设计师品牌参加：Pronounce、Private Policy（《智族》中国赞助）、Xander Zhou、Danshan、Feng Chen Wang。</p><p><strong>Danshan 和 Feng Chen Wang 在当地时间 1 月 6 日下午和 1 月 7 日分别以时装演示和走秀的形式发布了新系列。</strong></p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/mens-fall-collections-2019/london/danshan/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Danshan 2019 秋冬：</a></strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108125707zR4wN21HyLtoE03O.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901081257108yStuYFAQWwCL5J9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108125711igwvVlQqmMfIACHO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108125707qkgr9CMXUV4tTi72.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901081257080QXGOniBzW3Ey7g9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108125708cS1P5HyrW367psw8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108125708IJPZUyKvDGb3LM1Y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108125708klxjJT6UYbv53rRe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style